    "body": "The missing values are due to the block context being unavailable at the \"transaction\" level. In the case of `eth_getTransactionByBlockHashAndIndex` and `eth_getBlock`, the block is known and details can be added to the transaction.\n\nSomehow, the RPC needs to be able to look up a transaction hash and return the block number it is contained in. This information can be then added to the output.\n",
